confirmationMessage: We have sent you a confirmation message.

whatNext.title: What happens next?
whatNext.body: Your video and answers have been shared with your probation officer. They will contact you if there are any concerns with the information you've entered, or if you requested contact.
whatNext.reminder: We will remind you when it is time for your next check in.
